@83 = ~Shadow Touch
Any humanoid, giant humanoid, or animal hit by the spell must make a Saving Throw or is transformed into a mindless undead creature and put under control of the caster for one hour. Any creature not affected by the transformation or successfully making the Saving Throw still suffers 2d4 points of magic damage. Undead creatures, constructs, and creatures protected from death effects are immune to the spell.

The transformation into an undead creature is based on the caster's level:
  1st level: Target must save vs. Death or is transformed into a ghoul.
  9th level: Target must save vs. Death with a -2 penalty or is transformed into a ghast.
  17th level: Target must save vs. Death with a -4 penalty or is transformed into a wraith.
  25th level: Target must save vs. Death with a -6 penalty or is transformed into a vampiric wraith.~

