@200 = ~This black-bound tome is unpleasant to the touch and radiates a foul smell that stirs an uneasy feeling in your mind.~
@201 = ~The tome is covered in arcane symbols and written in unknown runes that trigger a feeling of dread and something even more terrifying that leaves a strange sensation in your mind. It does not open no matter how much you try.~
@202 = ~The tome is covered in arcane symbols and written in unknown runes that trigger a feeling of dread. It does not open no matter how much you try.~
@203 = ~Even after turning the tome away you can't do much but think of it for a while.~
@204 = ~As you're about to turn the tome away an irresistable feeling of malicious satisfaction overwhelms you. You know that something changed deep inside you.~
@205 = ~As you turn your attention to the tome a powerful force urges you to keep away from it. All your senses tell you that the tome would corrupt your soul just by examining it.~
